To update the .pot file:
$ ./update.sh

To add a new language to the repository:
$ ./add_lang.sh nl

To merge the .pot file with all methlab.po files:
$ ./merge.sh

To merge the .pot file with the nl/methlab.po file:
$ cd nl
$ ../merge.sh

To compile all methlab.po files to methlab.mo:
$ ./compile.sh

To compile the nl/methlab.po file to nl/methlab.mo:
$ cd nl
$ ../compile.sh
